76
00:05:27,670 --> 00:05:28,750
Ď-Ďakujem ti.

77
00:05:29,250 --> 00:05:30,210
T-To nestojí za reč.

78
00:05:35,090 --> 00:05:37,970
Také ponižujúce!

79
00:05:37,970 --> 00:05:40,100
